metadata.name: Reflecting Pool
metadata.description:
Washington D.C.  
COVID-19 Lockdown

Top - 4/27/20: Two bikers take a selfie to immortalize the emptiness of this usually high-traffic area during the lockdown of COVID-19.

Bottom - 11/27/20: Tourists and residents back outside enjoying the day around the Reflecting Pool as the world attempts a return to normalcy.
